title: Ciscos
extract: cisco - Computer Definition. (Cisco Systems, Inc., San Jose, CA, www.cisco.com) A leading manufacturer of networking equipment, including routers, bridges, frame switches and ATM switches, dial-up access servers and network management software. ... Initially targeting universities, Cisco sold its first router in 1986.
